{"tid":949153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本TG谷有意招收新成員","createTime":"2018-12-20T15:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T07:34:11.000Z","uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"434a2230baf0eb0b0bb77e184e1ce346baafb493","tid":949153,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"本谷都偏向熱鬧<br />\n經常幾百過千msg 隨時歡迎插嘴 <br />\n上至天文地理文學設計<br />\n下至18禁動漫打機出櫃<br />\n乜都歡迎大家9up一餐<br />\n成員包括大隻巴冗員氣質女神絲文青教師痴線佬淫娃乜都齊 <br />\n一定搵到你想識嘅朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本谷經常有群聚 <br />\n亦間中有小圈子小聚<br />\n（你以為有絲出？諗下好啦）<br />\n<br />\nAdmin會經常處決潛水員 <br />\n巴絲比例亦算達至黃金比例約99:1 (連登邊有咁多真絲)<br />\n<br />\n盡量希望大家Keep住有人氣 <br />\n亦冇乜特別規則要大家遵守 <br />\n只希望各位自重自律 <br />\n要搞小圈子 狗衝PM <br />\n只要對方唔投訴 話知你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但公然人身攻擊 <br />\n引起罵戰就唔好怪Admin <br />\n踢你都唔需要同你解釋啲乜 <br />\n開谷一年多 <br />\nAdmin踢人嘅次數唔多過5次 <br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單來講正正常常就歡迎你加入<br />\n你肯講就有人聽 <br />\n你痴線實有人陪你癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真撚 真心撚唔抽得水 玻璃心就慎重考慮 <br />\nTG谷好危險 唔岩你玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/BuddyHahaGroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBuddyHahaGroup&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=656100d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BuddyHahaGroup</a>"},{"pid":"e73aa4371a020e44079f969907e44b9dec6e5c77","tid":949153,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"而入<br />\n吃了唔少女🤤🤤"},{"pid":"943d3bae8be24485f8fba16aa5a8a0b37a1fb007","tid":949153,"uid":138134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f4a3a38f2ac0a6b23f11f56d3b1c5dcdd0585af3","tid":949153,"uid":38503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"